'''knife pleat'''

[[Image:Knife_pleat.jpg|thumb|right|200px|A series of knife pleats]]

# A type of sharply pressed [[pleat]]ing, esp. in a [[skirt]] or [[kilt]], in which all of the folds are turned in one direction, with each pleat being three (3) layers of fabric thick.

